doc.minimatch: : {{_glob_}} habka u dhigma, iyadoo la adeegsanayo {{_minimatch_}} maktabadda, habka isticmaalka <a href='https://github.com/isaacs/minimatch' target='_blank' rel='noreferrer'>fiiri < /a>, ama waxaad raadin kartaa {{_glob_}}
